This project interoperates with, but does NOT include or redistribute, any
proprietary Dreame firmware. The reverse-engineering notes in docs/FINDINGS.md
describe observed behavior, memory offsets, and data structures for the purpose
of interoperability. No decompiled source code or firmware binaries from Dreame
are distributed here.

To use the patcher you must supply your own `node_camera_ai.so`, extracted from
your own device. The resulting patched binary is a derivative of your device's
firmware and must remain on your own device.

